TopicTitle: To Mun and Back: The full series!

Articles.Content:
While I am far from the greatest Youtuber I thought I would share my videos here as well. In this first installment is my Mun landing, the second explanation in the video. The first video had some audio issues, and as such please make a note at the 2 minute mark of the warning to turn down the sound. If you like what you see hit that thumbs up button, and subscribe for more KSP hijinks! Now on with our show!! ...also a side note my voice during the time of these recordings was bad so I may sound raspy.
